We know that.

246
00:08:37,281 --> 00:08:38,692
那么，这样子说定了：
So here's the deal.

247
00:08:38,866 --> 00:08:42,033
你可以走了，不过我们会盯着你的
You're free to go,
but we will have eyes on you.

248
00:08:42,203 --> 00:08:45,619
不是一直，但是我们会在你最不希望出现的时候出现
Not always, but when
you least expect it, we'll be there.

249
00:08:45,790 --> 00:08:48,281
任何一个你想结交的人，甚至是交谈过的
Anyone you try to make friends with
or even talk to,

250
00:08:48,459 --> 00:08:50,914
反正是有过任何交集的人
other than ordering a hot dog
or something,

251
00:08:51,087 --> 00:08:55,250
