255
00:09:03,390 --> 00:09:05,050
就我个人来说，我不相信
Personally, I don't.

256
00:09:05,226 --> 00:09:07,432
所以，如果我是你，我宁愿去自杀
So I'd go for it if I were you.

257
00:09:10,815 --> 00:09:13,187
但是我不是你
But I am not you.

258
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:15,689
感谢上帝
Thank God.

259
00:09:15,861 --> 00:09:18,269
所以做你想做的事吧
So do what you want.

260
00:09:18,447 --> 00:09:20,938
如果你明天还在这，我们会杀掉房东
If you're still here tomorrow,
we're going to kill the landlady.

261
00:09:21,117 --> 00:09:23,654
- 她叫什么名字？
- 特巴洛斯基
- What was her name?
- Tobolovsky.

262
00:09:23,828 --> 00:09:25,986
特巴洛斯基夫人
Mrs Tobolovsky.

263
00:09:26,163 --> 00:09:28,156
很好
Nice lady.

264
00:09:29,166 --> 00:09:31,242
收拾一下吧，清洁工
Clean up the mess, garbage man.

265
00:09:36,882 --> 00:09:39,967
好了！她是你女儿，她也是美国公民
All right, she's your daughter
and she's an American citizen.

266
00:09:40,803 --> 00:09:43,923
我不会打听你们的关系，这是你们的事
I ain't gonna ask what the deal is
with her. That's your business.

267
00:09:44,807 --> 00:09:47,808
不过我想说的是，找关系是很困难的
But I'm gonna tell you,
pulling strings is hard work,

268
00:09:47,977 --> 00:09:49,934
困难的工作一般不会免费
and hard work don't come free.

269
00:09:52,481 --> 00:09:53,975
