I saw yourfight in Jersey.

280
00:10:49,997 --> 00:10:52,749
实在是太棒了，你轻松干掉了那家伙
It was really good.
You knocked that guy out.

281
00:10:52,917 --> 00:10:56,499
- 不是的
- 我有好东西，兄弟
- No.
- That was some good shit, man.

282
00:10:56,629 --> 00:10:58,621
很棒的格斗
Great fight.

283
00:11:48,347 --> 00:11:50,423
赌场呢？
The casino?

284
00:11:56,439 --> 00:11:58,680
80万整？
Exactly 800,000?

285
00:11:58,858 --> 00:12:00,850
大约80万
It's almost 800.

286
00:12:04,905 --> 00:12:06,862
我不是问你是不是大概80万
I'm not asking you if it's almost 800.

287
00:12:07,032 --> 00:12:09,025
我要准确数字
I want the exact number.

288
00:12:09,869 --> 00:12:13,238
78万5370美元
$785,370.

289
00:12:16,667 --> 00:12:19,953
- 再上一周呢？
- 在亏钱
- And the week before?
- It's losing money.

290
00:13:18,687 --> 00:13:20,230
- 怎么？
- 为什么？
- What?
- Why?

291
