00:14:55,367 --> 00:14:58,155
- 我不能...
- 闭嘴，闭嘴！
- I just... I can't take another...
- Shut up. Shut up.

305
00:15:00,498 --> 00:15:02,823
闭嘴，拿走吧，我还有旧鞋子
Shut up and take them.
I've still got my old ones.

306
00:15:05,211 --> 00:15:06,919
好好照顾你的脚
Go and get those feet looked at.

