00:15:08,839 --> 00:15:10,417
都烂掉了
Gangrene's setting in.

308
00:15:10,591 --> 00:15:13,462
我会的，谢谢你，朋友
I will. Thank you, man.

309
00:15:15,096 --> 00:15:18,180
上帝保佑你，兄弟，上帝保佑你
Jesus loves you, brother.
Jesus loves you.

310
00:15:25,481 --> 00:15:28,351
