Mister, I told you, if you don't
have money, you have to leave, OK?

342
00:19:24,887 --> 00:19:27,010
让开，还有人在等呢
You gotta get out of line.
People are waiting.

343
00:19:28,099 --> 00:19:30,257
走开，兄弟，让开
