梅，你是个孩子…我不确定自己能否做个好父亲
Mei, you're a kid and...
I'm not sure I could be a good father.

1000
01:26:12,603 --> 01:26:14,346
我想我能力不足
I think that ship has sailed.

1001
01:26:14,522 --> 01:26:16,431
我不想要父亲
I don't want no more fathers.

1002
01:26:18,901 --> 01:26:21,107
你可以做我朋友吗？
Will you be my friend?

1003
01:26:22,488 --> 01:26:24,481
至死都愿
Till my dying day.

1004
01:26:29,036 --> 01:26:32,452
我找到一家在西雅图专门培训天才儿童的学校
I got info on a school
for gifted kids up in Seattle.

1005
01:26:34,083 --> 01:26:37,666
这会是次美妙旅行，如果你喜欢那里的风光的话
It's a nice drive,
if you like trees and shit.

1006
01:26:39,964 --> 01:26:40,960
我们安全了吗？
Are we safe?

1007
01:26:43,259 --> 01:26:46,758
别想太多，梅，别想太多
One day at a time, Mei.
One day at a time.

